Adds a description of '-disable_syslog' option to
the manual page of the Erlang Port Mapper Daemon.

Not suitable for upstream.

--- otp_doc_man_28.4/man/man1/epmd.1
+++ otp_doc_man_28.4/man/man1/epmd.1
@@ -83,6 +83,12 @@ \fI-d\fR flags specified, the more debug
 
 .RE
 
+-disable_syslog
+.RS 2
+Disables logging when \fIepmd\fR\& is started as a daemon\&. Not recommended for the general use and production\&.
+
+.RE
+
 -daemon
 .RS 2
 Starts 
